by <a href="../../people/sarbit_b.shtml">Bruce Sarbit</a></p>
<p><a href="salvationarmy.shtml">&ldquo;Help for Manitoba&rsquo;s Farmers and Housewives&rdquo;: The Salvation Army as an Official Immigration Agency</a><br>
