by Meg Stanley</p>
<p><a href="/docs/mb_history/83/reviewrobertteigroblivingwithwar.shtml">Robert Teigrob, <em>Living with War: Twentieth-Century Conflict in Canadian &amp; American History and Memory</em></a><br>
